headline: Why Estée Lauder (EL) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of beauty products company Estée Lauder (NYSE:EL) jumped 3.5% in the afternoon session after an analyst at Evercore ISI Group reiterated a positive outlook on the company, raising the firm's price target.
